        <Parent_String>census districts [300250943], administrative districts [300000707], districts by function [300000706], districts [300000705], Built Complexes and Districts (hierarchy name) [300000201], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
